I found the main API endpoint for deepSeek at https://api.deepseek.com/chat/completions, which uses a POST method with a JSON body to create chat completions.

Regarding authentication, since you mentioned "Bearer Token," the connector group for deepSeek should use bearer token authentication with the "access_token" field.

Here is the suggested authentication configuration for deepSeek:

```json
{
  "type": "bearerToken",
  "details": {
    "expires_in": {
      "type": "number",
      "hidden": true,
      "default": 100000,
      "disabled": true
    },
    "access_token": {
      "type": "password",
      "required": true,
      "description": "Token"
    }
  }
}
```

I will now proceed to create the connector group "DeepSeek" with this bearer token auth configuration and then add the "createChatCompletion" endpoint.
